.’ It is also the first vampire book I wrote, and to be honest, one of the most detailed and fun books I have written. I believe that this ongoing saga is deep, engaging, and entertaining.\nHaving vampires run the show is pretty much representative of the governments that rule over us. This is one thing that differs in this vampire story when it is compared to others.\nCyril DeSai is a centuries-old vampire who has been wreaking havoc and causing terror in the hearts of men all over the world. While DeSai is nothing more than a black-hearted spawn of Satan. I wanted him to be loaded with such sex appeal and confidence that even his most morbid behaviors became easy to overlook. This was a bit difficult, because realistically, Cyril DeSai is a murderous vampire. But once Rasia comes onto the scene, this daunting task lightened a bit. Will the ‘victor’ become the victim? Now, the reader is able to sympathize with him on a different level, which honestly sets the tone for both of the next two books.\nIs this trilogy far-fetched? Of course! It’s a vampire story!<\/span>\n  <a data-text-id=\"17581017312501745278\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"swapContent(\$(this));; return false;\">...more<\/a>\n\n    <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\'wtrButtonContainer wtrSignedOut\' id=\'4_book_30367466\'>\n<div class=\'wtrUp wtrLeft\'>\n<form action=\"/shelf/add_to_shelf\" accept-charset=\"UTF-8\" method=\"post\"><input name=\"utf8\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"&#x2713;\" /><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"authenticity_token\" value=\"LZ5acp/Zp6jmOxJPzURjGZoG/8C1O215FMjwRNOllk/rTQTsPP92j9lmKtc+2LihY286vf+r9YBLvP1S3hyLJQ==\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_id\" id=\"book_id\" value=\"30367466\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"name\" id=\"name\" value=\"to-read\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"unique_id\" id=\"unique_id\" value=\"4_book_30367466\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"wtr_new\" id=\"wtr_new\" value=\"true\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_choice\" id=\"from_choice\" value=\